[section#range.single.overview
    [:en] Overview
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] [`single_view] produces a [`view] that contains exactly one element of a
specified value.
[:zh_CN] [`single_view] 产生刚好包含单个具有指定值的元素的 [`view]。

[para]
[begin:example]
[codeblock]
single_view s{4};
for (int i : s)
  cout << i;        // [:en] prints [`4] \
                       [:zh_CN] 打印 [`4]
[codeblock:end]
[end:example]
